47:19.160 --> 47:23.040
The issue of inequality and especially,

47:23.040 --> 47:24.960
well, some maybe somebody else said that too,

47:24.960 --> 47:28.440
that the rich got richer during the pandemic.

47:28.440 --> 47:32.440
I actually think inequality is a result

47:32.440 --> 47:35.560
of the fourth industrial revolution

47:35.560 --> 47:40.600
that we have been living in for a long time, actually.

47:40.600 --> 47:42.840
And now we see the big fruits of it

47:42.840 --> 47:46.280
because that industrial revolution meant

47:46.280 --> 47:50.800
that we use more machines, we use more software,

47:50.800 --> 47:55.000
we use more robots, and because they have become

47:55.000 --> 47:56.640
more productive over time.

47:57.880 --> 48:02.880
And the way that things work in a corporation

48:02.880 --> 48:06.840
or in any business, this productivity is attributed

48:06.840 --> 48:10.320
to capital and not to labor.

48:10.320 --> 48:12.800
And it's therefore paid to capital.

48:12.800 --> 48:16.280
And therefore, it shows up in profits.

48:16.280 --> 48:21.280
So if a labor is changed and replaced by a machine,

48:23.480 --> 48:26.920
then the amount of that goes to labor decreases

48:26.920 --> 48:31.040
and the amount that goes to capital and profits increases.

48:31.040 --> 48:36.040
So that almost automatically creates inequality.

48:36.520 --> 48:38.760
It's inequality at the corporate level,

48:38.760 --> 48:40.640
at the level of the business.

48:40.640 --> 48:44.880
But if you think that the owners of the capital

48:44.880 --> 48:47.640
are not the workers, then automatically it creates

48:47.640 --> 48:51.640
an inequality between the owners of the capital

48:51.640 --> 48:52.920
and the workers.

48:52.920 --> 48:55.400
And that's something that is there.

48:55.400 --> 48:58.320
I mean, we should really see for sure that way.

48:58.320 --> 49:01.600
And at least in my opinion, the way to fix it

49:01.600 --> 49:06.240
is to make sure that the workers have a part of the business,

49:06.240 --> 49:09.960
they have shares, they have a way to get

49:09.960 --> 49:13.400
to have an avenue of access to the profits

49:13.400 --> 49:14.680
of the corporation.

49:14.680 --> 49:18.000
It won't fix inequality across the board,

49:18.000 --> 49:20.800
but it will fix this particular inequality

49:20.800 --> 49:24.760
to some extent that comes from the foreign industrial revolution.

49:24.760 --> 49:27.120
It comes from the importance of the product,

49:27.120 --> 49:31.240
the increase in the productivity of machines and software.

49:31.240 --> 49:33.080
And I think that we should take it,

49:33.080 --> 49:34.320
at least from my point of view,

49:34.320 --> 49:40.040
we should think of ways for this to actually happen,

49:40.040 --> 49:45.160
which we might be able to implement at the corporate level

49:45.160 --> 49:50.600
and fix a significant part of the business.

